Dynamite opens with RUSH vs MJF in MJF's first match since 12/31

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/41e034f0-6704-4c2b-9b2c-2f446424532d/PhotoGrid_1_20240619170559.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_MJF DEF. RUSH_**
    

What a match!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/fe769eba-bfeb-479b-a6bd-eb923e9f4a95/20240619_172000.jpg?format=original)

Cage of Agony let’s MJF know that he’ll be taking on Hechicero at Forbidden Door!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e4860a78-d12a-4813-a919-49357014d49a/20240619_172815.jpg?format=original)

Will Ospreay and Swerve Strickland are face to face about their world championship match at Forbidden Door.

Will Ospreay is cocky heading into the match off of his current record over the last year. But Swerve isn’t here to play. The World Championship isn’t a game to him

He asks if Ospreay is willing to sacrifice everything the way Swerve has? Willing to sacrifice his love of pro wrestling, his friends even wife and his son?

Ospreay is furious. DO NOT MENTION HIS SON. Nana tries to calm this down and end the segment.

Will leaves the ring and Swerve calls him back.. WHAT IF I WANTED TO MAKE THIS PERSONAL?

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bd6e32e7-6a6b-4808-a970-3b1467587101/20240619_173852.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e38438c4-1107-4f85-b719-c964df475e8e/PhotoGrid_1_20240619174552.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_ALL STAR 8 MAN TAG MATCH: MARK BRISCOE, KYLE O'REILLY, DANTE MARTIN AND ORANGE CASSIDY KONOSUKE TAKESHITA, KYLE FLETCHER, RODERICK STRONG AND ZACK SABRE JR_**
    

Very fun, PWG style faced pace match. Kyle O'Reilly pushed Orange Cassidy out of the way to take a knee for him. Cassidy rebounds with an Orange Punch for the win over Roderick Strong

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3fb14467-7da6-453f-bff6-1c2b990a4162/PhotoGrid_1_20240619181027.jpg?format=original)

It appears Don Callis is offering RUSH a spot in the Family

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e0d93e39-9569-4e70-978e-4fdb34d74b42/20240619_180517.jpg?format=original)

Okada cuts off the Acclaimed before they could rap because he “hit the wrong button”

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/64fa5fb9-710a-4906-9238-e4dcd76b9895/20240619_180515.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7f1a99f0-733b-4a3a-8bb2-c372963ee8c3/20240619_181800.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_AEW WORLD TAG TEAM TITLE ELIMINATOR: THE ACCLAIMED DEF. THE YOUNG BUCKS_**
    

Anthony Bowens worked most of the match alone as the Bucks kept taking out Max Caster. Eventually the Bucks try to cheat with title belts. Matt gets caught. Nick knocks out Matt while Rick Knox is distracted. Bowens and Caster take advantage, hit their finish for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e87a5747-bd77-4ff0-99c7-1ce01c0ecbb9/20240619_182147.jpg?format=original)

Mariah May tries to tell both girls she loves them before they start signing contracts.

Mina tells Mariah to shut up! Mina says in STARDOM, Toni Storm is a legend. In AEW, Toni Storm became a Star. But as Champion? Toni’s gotten soft. At Forbidden Door, Mina is going to take Toni's Championship and her girl.

Toni says if Mina every raises her voice at Mariah again, she’ll slap her title off.

Mina tells Mariah she’s gonna have to choose between her and Toni Storm.

Saraya, Anna Jay and Harley Cameron attack all three women before they could continue. Toni gets taken out while Mariah gets saved by Mina. Toni is alone in the ring.

* * *

